      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=ekr2ncu8aq]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ekr2ncu8aq]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=gcrfx7wb5i]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=gcrfx7wb5i]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=y9i2w6fah3]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=y9i2w6fah3]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"gcrfx7wb5i\">Resource</span></strong>: HDRI</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ekr2ncu8aq\">Captured by</span></strong>: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://www.dylansisson.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dylan Sisson</a></p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"y9i2w6fah3\">Use</span></strong>: Attach this map to a PxrDomeLight</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://assets.renderman.pixar.com/resources/luxo_jr_hdri/373_192_luxo_jr_hdr.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608567297/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285409156&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608567297/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285409156&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608567342\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"608567297\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c93652cb-67a7-4d5e-8d00-d6b89b6774ab\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608567297/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285409156&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608567297/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285409156&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"LuxoJr.-Overview\">Overview</h1><p>Location: Pixar Animation Studios</p><p>This HDRI was captured at the main campus of Pixar Animation Studios. Feel free to use it whenever you require a panorama with a giant lamp.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"337_194_luxo_jr_2000x2000.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/608567297/337_194_luxo_jr_2000x2000.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285472033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=760\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/608567297/337_194_luxo_jr_2000x2000.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758285472033&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"2000\" data-width=\"2000\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"607945056\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-